OL,5, Pope Francis has called on European    
OL,6, nations to show greater tolerance      
OL,7, towards migrants during a visit to the 
OL,8, southern French city of Marseille.     
OL,10,FSpeaking at a meeting of bishops and   
OL,11,Fyoung people from Mediterranean        
OL,12,Fcountries, the pontiff said "those who 
OL,13,Frisk their lives at sea do not invade".
OL,15,FFrench President Emmanuel Macron was   
OL,16,Famong the audience for the address.    
OL,18,FIt comes as the migration debate has   
OL,19,Fbeen reignited by mass arrivals on the 
OL,20,FItalian island of Lampedusa last week. 
